        Bridging Finance When Buying and Selling in Brisbane: What Sellers Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        What bridging finance actually is, how the numbers work, the risks that rarely get explained clearly, and the alternatives that suit Brisbane's market conditions.
      </p>
